text:
When parsing web.xml I get an error after anything bellow the session-config 
tag.

Not enough information to identify any problem.  What web.xml file were you
trying to process?  What error messages were logged?

One thing to check is that your web.xml file conforms to the element ordering
requirements of the DTD -- the order is very specific, and any violation will
cause an XML parsing failure (which will make your app unavailable).
